{"tid":1998304,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"五眼聯盟情報文件流出 指中國有意隱瞞武漢肺炎疫情 導致數以萬計既人死亡","createTime":"2020-05-02T09:58:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T11:12:37.000Z","uid":48083,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"daf621cc124386d2c091f87559957f5e0aa65463","tid":1998304,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T09:58:23.000Z","msg":"Leaked Western intel dossier reveals how China deceived the world about coronavirus<br />\nBy Nick Givas, Samuel Chamberlain | Fox News<br />\n<br />\nA research dossier compiled by the so-called &quot;Five Eyes&quot; intelligence alliance states that China intentionally hid or destroyed evidence of the coronavirus outbreak, leading to the loss of tens of thousands of lives around the world<br />\n<br />\nThe 15-page document from the intelligence agencies of the U.S., Canada, the U.K., Australia and New Zealand, was obtained by Australia's Saturday Telegraph newspaper and states that China's secrecy amounted to an &ldquo;assault on international transparency.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/world/new-dossier-condemns-china-for-destroying-evidence-of-covid-19-outbreak\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fworld%2Fnew-dossier-condemns-china-for-destroying-evidence-of-covid-19-outbreak&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=0c849634\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fworld%2Fnew-dossier-condemns-china-for-destroying-evidence-of-covid-19-outbreak&h=8bca7f0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.foxnews.com/world/new-dossier-condemns-china-for-destroying-evidence-of-covid-19-outbreak</a><br />\n<br />\nTelegraph最先爆出嚟，詳細內容：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dailytelegraph.com.au/coronavirus/bombshell-dossier-lays-out-case-against-chinese-bat-virus-program/news-story/55add857058731c9c71c0e96ad17da60\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailytelegraph.com.a